    <note>Zhao(1) Huan(2) [9009] Huizong's [9008] eldest son, Gaozong's [9010] brother. His empress, the Renhuai huanghou Zhu(1) Shi [4219], was the sister of the father of Jiang(2) Hao's wife. Hao [3227], in turn, was the father of Jiang(2) Yu [3228], the betrothed of Wang(1) Siwen's [1758] granddaughter. Hao's wife's grandfather was also the brother of Zhao(1) Shenzong's [9006] second empress, the Qincheng huanghou Zhu(1) Shi [4218]. CBD, 1, 778-9.</note>
